## Local development

```bash
cd backend
npm install

# Point at your local service account key + GCP project
$env:GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS = "C:\path\to\sa-key.json"
$env:GCP_PROJECT_ID = "attendance-tracker-490319"
$env:GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID = "..."
$env:OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET_NAME = "projects/829771833968/secrets/oauth-client-secret"
$env:SECRET_NAME = "projects/829771833968/secrets/service-account-key"
$env:SESSION_SECRET = "32-byte-base64-secret"

npm start
# Server runs on http://localhost:8080
```

For env var details and the full list see the [top-level README](../README.md#backend-env-vars-cloud-run).

